comments.content: The neon script looks like it’s based on [Ray Larabie](http://web.archive.org/web/20080720062530/http:/www.typophile.com/wiki/Ray%252BLarabie)’s [Deftone Stylus](http://web.archive.org/web/20080720062530/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/larabie/deftone/).
There are a couple of usual suspects for the stencil face (Identikal and such), but I unfortunately haven’t got time right now to go hunting for it. :^/
